{
  "3003050": {
    "name": "地球上的罗伯特",
    "steam_appid": 3003050,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/b0714007937511d42f9920ae1ace0a76.avif?t=1767075908\" width=625 height=260 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这是一款剧情驱动的横版末日废土种田游戏。不久的将来，地球资源枯竭、有机生命被冰冷的机械世界所取代。但在阴暗的废墟深处，依然潜藏着一丝绿色的希望。你将扮演一台迷茫而可爱的小机器人，亲手在地底开辟一方绿洲。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/b4c52f9da4892d515b5c33937ca64846.poster.avif?t=1767075908\" width=604 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/b4c52f9da4892d515b5c33937ca64846.webm?t=1767075908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/b4c52f9da4892d515b5c33937ca64846.mp4?t=1767075908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/57705595ec1f39f2502d468761b6f120.avif?t=1767075908\" width=616 height=154 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从一片死寂的废土中开垦出属于你的地下绿洲！利用地球上最后的资源，从种植提供生存能量的奇异小草开始，精心照料每一株拥有顽强生命力的奇特作物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/acf95db5288ed2fecd9e92374c668bb3.poster.avif?t=1767075908\" width=600 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/acf95db5288ed2fecd9e92374c668bb3.webm?t=1767075908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/acf95db5288ed2fecd9e92374c668bb3.mp4?t=1767075908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合理规划布局，巧妙搭配不同作物的特性，构建高效而神奇的地下农场生产系统，让生机在这片荒漠之下重新流淌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/743c043398602a282a64446904e47372.poster.avif?t=1767075908\" width=600 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/743c043398602a282a64446904e47372.webm?t=1767075908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/743c043398602a282a64446904e47372.mp4?t=1767075908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为田地围上栅栏，摆放休憩的长椅，将冒险中收获的独特装饰布置起来，亲手装点你的家园！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/3459f02ca781ebb00886b2c0e1bdd8a7.poster.avif?t=1767075908\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/3459f02ca781ebb00886b2c0e1bdd8a7.webm?t=1767075908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/3459f02ca781ebb00886b2c0e1bdd8a7.mp4?t=1767075908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/96059d4244bd3ef3955eaba19ff057c7.avif?t=1767075908\" width=616 height=154 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个机械世界中，作物不再是传统的植物，而是齿轮、木板、灯泡等奇特的作物。每种作物都拥有独特的能力和生长特性。通过研究和培育，你可以解锁作物的变异形态，让它们产生意想不到的效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/6a7c411ae4b9d688f798a078218af699.poster.avif?t=1767075908\" width=600 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/6a7c411ae4b9d688f798a078218af699.webm?t=1767075908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/6a7c411ae4b9d688f798a078218af699.mp4?t=1767075908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用农场产出的资源，合成多样化的功能道具和素材。制造能够提升效率、解锁新功能的奇妙装置，让你的地下农场更加强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时，深入神秘矿坑采掘珍稀矿石，在地下水域垂钓变异鱼类。这些探索所得不仅是珍贵素材，更是强化罗伯特自身、获得永久能力提升的核心资源。解锁能量存储、远程操控、快速传送等能力，让你的小机器人不断进化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/e892816357d41372c4ec9372f7efbd48.poster.avif?t=1767075908\" width=600 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/e892816357d41372c4ec9372f7efbd48.webm?t=1767075908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/e892816357d41372c4ec9372f7efbd48.mp4?t=1767075908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/314d41c8f54f18fef7ef83d966aae4f2.avif?t=1767075908\" width=616 height=154 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏出农场，深入广阔而神秘的地底世界！从破败的荒漠小镇到象征机械文明顶峰的“永恒城”，游戏中有着各种各样奇妙的场景等待着你前去探索。开辟新道路，发现未知区域，每一次探索都充满惊喜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/3bbbf6029c5f3770476c2e039d271a68.poster.avif?t=1767075908\" width=602 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/3bbbf6029c5f3770476c2e039d271a68.webm?t=1767075908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/3bbbf6029c5f3770476c2e039d271a68.mp4?t=1767075908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在冒险中，你将遇见形形色色的机器人居民。有的将成为你并肩前行的可靠伙伴，分享知识与资源；有的则可能成为你前进路上的阻碍。每一次互动都推动着剧情发展，丰富你的冒险体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/2572d9bcdd14250a40aabf36012cc159.poster.avif?t=1767075908\" width=600 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/2572d9bcdd14250a40aabf36012cc159.webm?t=1767075908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/2572d9bcdd14250a40aabf36012cc159.mp4?t=1767075908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接受任务与挑战，深入险象环生的矿坑，在风沙肆虐的沙漠寻找绿洲，在深蓝水域探寻宝藏。一步步解开埋藏在废土深处的巨大谜团：地球为何变成这样？罗伯特的身世与记忆又隐藏着什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/bc6537de6b32fd0327739480f9c8e6e1.avif?t=1767075908\" width=625 height=260 /></span></p>",
